      "Title": "Botas.BotApp",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Botas.BotApp.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Zero-boilerplate bot host that wraps ASP.NET Core setup.</p>\n<p>\n<example>\n<pre><code class=\"lang-csharp\">var app = BotApp.Create(args);\napp.On(\"message\", async (ctx, ct) =&gt;\n    await ctx.SendAsync($\"Echo: {ctx.Activity.Text}\", ct));\napp.Run();</code></pre>\n</example>\n</p>\n"
    },
